<https://w3id.org/soel/test/SequenceMatchRatio> a ftr:Test.
    
<https://w3id.org/soel/benchmark/ALL> a ftr:Benchmark;
    dcterms:title "OntologyEngineeringEvaluationBenchmark"@en ;
    dcterms:description "comprehensive evaluation frameworks for assessing how well large language models (LLMs) can generate and match ontology concepts and properties against standard ontology definitions."@en .